# math.curve — pure-Simple elliptic curve operations.
#
# Built on the `math.field` layer (Fe25519, FeP256). Each curve module
# is a monomorphized specialization — no runtime dispatch on the field.
#
# Modules:
#   montgomery.spl  — Montgomery x-only ladder step (generic helper).
#   curve25519.spl  — X25519 DH (RFC 7748) using Fe25519.
#   edwards.spl     — Extended Edwards point arithmetic (generic helper).
#   ed25519.spl     — Ed25519 signatures (RFC 8032) using Fe25519.
#
# Usage:
#   use std.math.curve.curve25519.{x25519, x25519_base}
#   use std.math.curve.ed25519.{ed25519_sign, ed25519_verify, ed25519_keypair_from_seed}
#
# Constant-time: all scalar multiplications use fixed-iteration loops
# with `fe_cond_select` / `fe_cond_swap` (XOR-mask pattern). No branch
# on secret bits.
#
# No new externs — pure Simple only.
